# The contact form is handled by a Cloudflare Pages Function
# (functions/api/submit-contact-form.ts) which calls Resend directly.
#
# These secrets are NOT used by the frontend. Set them in your
# Cloudflare Pages project under Settings > Environment variables
# (Production and Preview):
#
#   RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxx
#   RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY=6LeXXXXXXXXXX
#
# This .env file is only needed if you add Vite-side env vars in future.
